      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"3. CLASSIC TEARS has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 3rd at this track over 320m. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Top chance in this line up. 1. BEATS PER MINUTE is suited by the inside draw. Last start finished 7th in a Grade 5 on March 30 over 365m at Nowra behind Cumbria Rich beaten 3.5 lengths (21.47). Looks well placed here and among the chances. 5. LIZZY BONKERS has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 18.46 beating Glimmer Girl. Must be included in calculations. 6. RED ROCK ALONG hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Grade 5 at this track over 320m. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a tricky draw.\",\"runners\":[3,1,5,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
